So yeah, want to speak to the type hint type information aspect of this whole thing?

00:54:17.840 --> 00:54:28.720
Well, essentially, as I mentioned, Stripe did it using simply dictionaries, and it was mostly untyped.

00:54:28.780 --> 00:54:41.420
As probably many people know, Stripe, after having so many problems with scalability in terms of the team scalability and problems with typing,

